6.Jun Hong, Lihu Liu, Ziwei Zhang, Xiange Xia*, Li Yang, Zengping Ning, Chengshuai Liu,Guohong Qiu*, Sulfate-accelerated photochemical oxidation of arsenopyrite in acidic systems under oxic conditions: Formation and function of schwertmannite,Journal of Hazardous Materials, 2022, 433, 128716. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jhazmat.2022.128716
